    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Biochem Engineering:</strong> 14th level</em></p>\n<p>As a reaction when you take damage from a creature within 15 feet of you that you can see, you can use one of your mixtures. The effects of the mixture release in a 15-foot-radius sphere centered on you, and if the mixture requires a saving throw, you automatically succeed on it. Additionally, the affected area is difficult terrain to creatures other than you until the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>Once you've used this feature, you must complete a short or long rest before you can use it again.</p>",
